public interface Processor extends org.elasticsearch.common.io.stream.NamedWriteable
A Processor evaluates locally an expression. For instance, ABS(foo). Aggregate functions are handled by ES but scalars are not. This is an opaque class, the computed/compiled result gets saved on the client during scrolling.
